OL,5,G0400 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,6,     FSally finds God and a somewhat
OL,7,     Fdubious spiritual guide.
OL,8,     FMeanwhile, divorce is on the cards
OL,9,     Ffor George and something even
OL,10,     Fnastier is on the cards for Dave.
OL,11,G0430 Stereo Underground
OL,12,     FRichard Latto presents alternative
OL,13,     Fanthems from a music community
OL,14,     Fwith attitude.
OL,15,G0530 Further Out of Town
OL,16,     FJack finds a little piece of
OL,17,     Fcountry life in the centre of
OL,18,     FLondon and buys himself a harness.
OL,19,     FFurther afield, he visits the
OL,20,     Fwaters of the Hebrides ahead of
OL,21,     Fthe annual fishing competition.
